# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We pledge to make participation in this project a harassment-free experience for everyone.

## Expected Behavior
- Be respectful and inclusive.
- Provide constructive feedback.
- Focus on collaboration and learning.

## Unacceptable Behavior
- Harassment, bullying, or discrimination.
- Personal attacks or abusive language.
- Sharing private information without permission.

## Enforcement
Project maintainers are responsible for clarifying and enforcing these standards.

## Reporting
Please report unacceptable behavior to the project maintainer through repository issues.
